titles.title: Electing Members and Delegates to certain standing committees of the House of Representatives.

vote.text: On agreeing to the resolution Agreed to by voice vote.

bill.summary: 1/18/2007--Passed House without amendment. (This measure has not been amended since it was introduced. The summary of that version is repeated here.) Elects majority Members to the House Committees on: (1) Armed Services; (2) Financial Services; (3) the Judiciary; (4) Natural Resources; (5) Science and Technology; and (6) Veterans' Affairs.
